# NorthernSovereigntyModule

**Dene-built resilience for the North.**  
Portable power (dual biodiesel generators), vertical farming (waste-heat fed), SatShield comms, and Nova Agora on-chain voting — all in a shipping container.

**Off-the-shelf parts. No grid. No wait.**  
Self-sovereignty starts here.

---

### Future Upgrade
**Phase 2:** Replace biodiesel with microreactor core — zero emissions, 20-year runtime.

